  <brief_title>Levetiracetam in Chronic Neuropathic Pain Following Spinal Cord Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Levetiracetam on Chronic Neuropathic Pain Following Spinal Cord Injury: a Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Cross-over, Multi-center Study</official_title>
