  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  1. age 18 or more

          -  2. neuropathic pain (that have lasted at least 3 month) after a spinal cord injury
             with a pain intensity of at least 4 on a 0-10 point numeric rating scale

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  1. pregnancy or lactation

          -  2. allergy to levetiracetam

          -  3. alcohol or substance abuse, mental disease, epilepsy, depression and psychiatric
             disorders, severe liver disease, decreased kidney function, and known concomitant
             cerebral damage
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
